
zenphoto installation instructions
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Edit the config.php.example file with your database and other info.

2. If you want to use mod_rewrite for cruft-free URLs, edit the one line of .htaccess

3. Get the files in the zenphoto.zip or zenphoto.tar.gz package on to your
   server somehow (FTP, SSH, wget, tar -xzvf .., etc.)
   
4. Go to http://www.yoursite.com/zenphoto/zen/setup.php and follow the
   simple instructions.